            "induction_speech": "The third number to be retired is #92. N, joined the typhoons last second right before their first season in pro. N played in challenger and IM all his career. People were skeptical if N would be able to compete in pro. He showed what he was able to do by putting up 71 points with 24 goals and 47 assists. N hanged up the skates with the typhoons and will not be seen soon."
